# Documentation & Examples Theme

All documentation and examples use a consistent theme around **motorcycle adventure photography**.

## Target Audience

The user is an adventure motorcycle rider and photographer who:
- Attends enduro training events
- Participates in motorcycle rallies and meets
- Takes motorcycle holidays / tours
- Photographs at off-road and adventure events

